article.description: — Jordan Sears scored 27 points as UT Martin beat Chicago State 94-71 on Saturday.
article.headline: UT Martin wins 94-71 over Chicago State
article.linkText: UT Martin wins 94-71 over Chicago State
article.story: CHICAGO -- — Jordan Sears scored 27 points as UT Martin beat Chicago State 94-71 on Saturday. Sears added five rebounds for the Skyhawks (5-2). Jacob Crews added 25 points and eight rebounds. The Cougars (2-6) were led by Wesley Cardet Jr., who posted 26 points. Kedrick Green added 15 points and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
